OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening to bring periods of rain,
OL,7,Fwith some heavier outbreaks late
OL,8,Fevening and during the early hours of
OL,9,FWednesday, before turning patchy
OL,10,Ftowards dawn. Strong southerly winds
OL,11,Feasing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FMainly cloudy with the odd
OL,14,Fshower possible, mainly in the morning
OL,15,Fwith the afternoon staying dry.
OL,16,FSoutherly winds occasionally fresh
OL,17,Facross Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
