OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FPeriods of rain Thursday, clearing to
OL,7,Fshowers late in the day. Friday mainly
OL,8,Fdry, occasionally bright, but gales
OL,9,Fand rain expected late in day.
OL,10,FSaturday windy and occasionally wet.
